[English subtitles are available]

2
00:00:48,610 --> 00:00:52,080
[Miss You Forever]

3
00:00:52,390 --> 00:00:54,700
[Episode 1]

4
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,350
Sister.

5
00:01:35,560 --> 00:01:38,759
This time, it's a first class order from the Grim Reapers.

6
00:01:45,900 --> 00:01:51,430
Bamboo forest on the outskirts of the city. The Sea Chart has appeared. Take the Chart and kill them.

7
00:02:36,110 --> 00:02:37,310
I don't let what I want

8
00:02:37,920 --> 00:02:39,720
fall into other people's hands.

9
00:02:41,910 --> 00:02:43,510
If you refuse to give it to me,

10
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:45,050
then trade your life for it.

11
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:10,840
I've been around the martial arts world for years,

12
00:03:10,840 --> 00:03:12,240
and I hate lying the most.

13
00:03:12,790 --> 00:03:13,920
I'll count to three.

14
00:03:14,110 --> 00:03:14,580
Tell me.

15
00:03:15,200 --> 00:03:16,460
Where is the Sea Chart?

16
00:03:19,030 --> 00:03:20,310
Here's the Chart.

17
00:03:20,720 --> 00:03:21,520
Spare me.

18
00:03:21,800 --> 00:03:22,630
The person you're looking for

19
00:03:22,630 --> 00:03:24,030
is in this forest.

20
00:03:25,820 --> 00:03:26,750
Before you came,

21
00:03:27,010 --> 00:03:29,040
a woman already took it.

22
00:03:34,620 --> 00:03:37,140
You're always ditching me.

23
00:03:37,790 --> 00:03:40,630
What if something happens to you?

24
00:03:41,460 --> 00:03:43,160
What nonsense are you talking about?

25
00:03:43,160 --> 00:03:44,760
You'll do what you need to do.

26
00:03:47,670 --> 00:03:48,600
Someone is here.

27
00:04:24,060 --> 00:04:25,060
She can't die yet.

28
00:04:42,400 --> 00:04:42,990
Oh no.

29
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:59,550
[One month ago]

30
00:05:10,330 --> 00:05:10,860
Great.

31
00:05:12,440 --> 00:05:13,960
Nice dance. Nice.

32
00:05:17,140 --> 00:05:17,980
So beautiful.

33
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:37,840
[Merchant Xie Jingshu]

34
00:05:41,080 --> 00:05:42,880
Young Master, the guest is here.

35
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,350
Over there! Go! Stop!

36
00:06:01,440 --> 00:06:03,160
The top courtesan of Jiangzhou.

37
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:04,820
You deserve your reputation.

38
00:06:05,660 --> 00:06:08,450
Greetings, Mr. Xie, I'm Bai Rui.

39
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:24,880
Please enjoy, Mr. Xie.

40
00:06:36,440 --> 00:06:38,570
Mr. Xie, you're having such fun today.

41
00:06:38,950 --> 00:06:40,750
Why didn't you ask me to join you?

42
00:06:45,920 --> 00:06:46,720
You may leave.

43
00:06:49,350 --> 00:06:50,040
Yes.

44
00:07:07,290 --> 00:07:10,100
What? She's not enough for you, Mr. Xie?

45
00:07:13,870 --> 00:07:16,870
If you had gone one inch lower, I'll have no offspring.

46
00:07:23,380 --> 00:07:24,310
It's beautiful,

47
00:07:25,500 --> 00:07:26,750
but it's not what I love.

48
00:07:26,750 --> 00:07:27,190
You...

49
00:07:29,030 --> 00:07:30,290
The real guest is here.

50
00:08:15,350 --> 00:08:16,410
Change clothes with me.

51
00:08:16,410 --> 00:08:17,540
I'll distract them.

52
00:08:35,520 --> 00:08:36,850
Over there! After them!

53
00:08:59,650 --> 00:09:00,910
There is danger ahead.

54
00:09:05,870 --> 00:09:07,070
It should be safe now.

55
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:22,670
Well...

56
00:09:46,910 --> 00:09:47,620
This time,

57
00:09:49,090 --> 00:09:50,420
let me help you instead.

58
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:14,090
[The Xie Residence]

59
00:10:46,260 --> 00:10:47,340
I need an identity.

60
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:49,000
I want

61
00:10:49,770 --> 00:10:51,030
to stay in the capital.

62
00:10:51,810 --> 00:10:53,010
I want you to marry me.

63
00:10:53,910 --> 00:10:55,310
We'll make a 100-day pact

64
00:10:56,590 --> 00:10:58,250
and I'll give you an identity.

65
00:10:58,700 --> 00:10:59,830
After the time is up,

66
00:11:00,730 --> 00:11:01,700
I'll say goodbye to you.
